{"title":"Home Ownership Calculator","description":"Calculate the true cost of owning a home — mortgage, taxes, insurance, HOA, and maintenance over 30 years.","url":"https://urcity.com/tools/home-ownership-calculator/","content":"\u003ch2 id=\"home-ownership-calculator\"\u003eHome Ownership Calculator\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBuying a home is more than just a mortgage payment. See the full picture with our True Cost of Home Ownership calculator.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"calculator-widget\" id=\"home-calc\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-header\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-icon green\"\u003e\n      \u003csvg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\n        \u003cpath d=\"M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"/\u003e\n        \u003cpolyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\"/\u003e\n      \u003c/svg\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-title-group\"\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003eTrue Cost of Home Ownership\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \u003cp class=\"calc-subtitle\"\u003eSee what you'll really pay over 30 years\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-inputs-row three-col\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"home-price\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cline x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Home Price\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-prefix\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"prefix\"\u003e$\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"home-price\" value=\"450000\" min=\"0\" step=\"10000\"\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"down-payment\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18\"/\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"17 6 23 6 23 12\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Down Payment\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"down-payment\" value=\"20\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" step=\"5\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"field-hint\" id=\"down-payment-hint\"\u003e$90,000 down\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"interest-rate\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cline x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Interest Rate\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"interest-rate\" value=\"6.5\" min=\"0\" max=\"20\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-inputs-row three-col\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"tax-rate\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z\"/\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Property Tax Rate\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"tax-rate\" value=\"1.8\" min=\"0\" max=\"5\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"hoa\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003crect x=\"2\" y=\"7\" width=\"20\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        HOA / Month\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-prefix\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"prefix\"\u003e$\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"hoa\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" step=\"50\"\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-elec\" value=\"135\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-water\" value=\"75\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-net\" value=\"55\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-trash\" value=\"30\"\u003e\n\n  \u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary btn-large\" onclick=\"calculateHome()\"\u003e\n    \u003csvg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n    Calculate Total Cost\n  \u003c/button\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-result\" id=\"home-result\" style=\"display:none;\"\u003e\n\n    \n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-tabs\"\u003e\n      \u003cbutton class=\"calc-tab active\" onclick=\"switchTab('tab-home')\" id=\"tab-btn-home\"\u003eHome Costs\u003c/button\u003e\n      \u003cbutton class=\"calc-tab\" onclick=\"switchTab('tab-monthly')\" id=\"tab-btn-monthly\"\u003eMonthly + Utilities\u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-tab-panel active\" id=\"tab-home\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"result-header\"\u003e\n        \u003ch4\u003eCost Breakdown\u003c/h4\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"result-badge badge-neutral\"\u003e30-Year Estimate\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-cards\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-card\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-label\"\u003eMonthly Payment\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-amount\" id=\"total-monthly\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-sub\"\u003ePrincipal + interest + taxes + insurance + HOA\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-card highlight\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-label\"\u003eTotal 30-Year Cost\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-amount\" id=\"total-cost\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-sub\"\u003eIncluding down payment and all fees\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"cost-breakdown\"\u003e\n        \u003ch5\u003eWhere Your Money Goes\u003c/h5\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#2563eb\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Mortgage (Principal + Interest)\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mortgage\" style=\"background:#2563eb\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mortgage\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#f59e0b\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Property Taxes\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-tax\" style=\"background:#f59e0b\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-tax\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#10b981\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Home Insurance\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-insurance\" style=\"background:#10b981\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-insurance\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#8b5cf6\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            HOA Fees\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-hoa\" style=\"background:#8b5cf6\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-hoa\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#ef4444\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Down Payment\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-down\" style=\"background:#ef4444\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-down\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"result-summary\" id=\"home-insight\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-tab-panel\" id=\"tab-monthly\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"result-header\"\u003e\n        \u003ch4\u003eMonthly Cost Breakdown\u003c/h4\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"result-badge badge-neutral\"\u003ePer Month\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-cards\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-card\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-label\"\u003eHome Ownership\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-amount\" id=\"monthly-home\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-sub\"\u003eMortgage + taxes + insurance + HOA\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-card highlight\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-label\"\u003eTotal Monthly\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-amount\" id=\"monthly-total\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"cost-summary-sub\"\u003eHome ownership + utilities\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"cost-breakdown\"\u003e\n        \u003ch5\u003eHome Ownership\u003c/h5\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#2563eb\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Mortgage (P+I)\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-mortgage\" style=\"background:#2563eb\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-mortgage\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#f59e0b\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Property Tax\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-tax\" style=\"background:#f59e0b\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-tax\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#10b981\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Home Insurance\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-insurance\" style=\"background:#10b981\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-insurance\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#8b5cf6\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            HOA Fees\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-hoa\" style=\"background:#8b5cf6\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-hoa\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003ch5 style=\"margin-top:1.5rem\"\u003eUtilities\u003c/h5\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#f97316\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Electricity\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-elec\" style=\"background:#f97316\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-elec\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#06b6d4\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Water\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-water\" style=\"background:#06b6d4\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-water\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#84cc16\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Internet\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-net\" style=\"background:#84cc16\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-net\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-row\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-label\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan class=\"breakdown-dot\" style=\"background:#a855f7\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n            Garbage / Trash\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar-track\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-bar\" id=\"bar-mo-trash\" style=\"background:#a855f7\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"breakdown-value\" id=\"val-mo-trash\"\u003e$0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"result-summary\" id=\"monthly-insight\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\nconst homePriceInput = document.getElementById('home-price');\nconst downPaymentInput = document.getElementById('down-payment');\nfunction updateDownHint() {\n  const price = parseFloat(homePriceInput.value) || 0;\n  const pct = parseFloat(downPaymentInput.value) || 0;\n  const amount = Math.round(price * (pct / 100));\n  document.getElementById('down-payment-hint').textContent = '$' + amount.toLocaleString() + ' down';\n}\nhomePriceInput.addEventListener('input', updateDownHint);\ndownPaymentInput.addEventListener('input', updateDownHint);\nupdateDownHint();\n\nfunction switchTab(tabId) {\n  \n  document.querySelectorAll('.calc-tab').forEach(btn =\u003e btn.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById('tab-btn-' + tabId.replace('tab-', '')).classList.add('active');\n  \n  document.querySelectorAll('.calc-tab-panel').forEach(panel =\u003e panel.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');\n}\n\nfunction calculateHome() {\n  const price = parseFloat(document.getElementById('home-price').value);\n  const downPercent = parseFloat(document.getElementById('down-payment').value);\n  const rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('interest-rate').value);\n  const taxRate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tax-rate').value);\n  const hoa = parseFloat(document.getElementById('hoa').value);\n\n  \n  const utilElec = parseFloat(document.getElementById('util-elec').value) || 0;\n  const utilWater = parseFloat(document.getElementById('util-water').value) || 0;\n  const utilNet = parseFloat(document.getElementById('util-net').value) || 0;\n  const utilTrash = parseFloat(document.getElementById('util-trash').value) || 0;\n  const totalUtilities = utilElec + utilWater + utilNet + utilTrash;\n\n  const downPayment = price * (downPercent / 100);\n  const loanAmount = price - downPayment;\n  const monthlyRate = rate / 100 / 12;\n  const numPayments = 30 * 12;\n\n  const mortgage = loanAmount * (monthlyRate * Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments)) / (Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments) - 1);\n  const tax = (price * (taxRate / 100)) / 12;\n  const insurance = (price * 0.0035) / 12;\n  const totalMonthly = mortgage + tax + insurance + hoa;\n\n  const totalMortgage = mortgage * numPayments;\n  const totalTax = tax * numPayments;\n  const totalInsurance = insurance * numPayments;\n  const totalHoa = hoa * numPayments;\n  const totalCost = totalMortgage + totalTax + totalInsurance + totalHoa + downPayment;\n\n  \n  document.getElementById('total-monthly').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalMonthly).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('total-cost').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalCost).toLocaleString();\n\n  document.getElementById('val-mortgage').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalMortgage).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-tax').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalTax).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-insurance').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalInsurance).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-hoa').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalHoa).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-down').textContent = '$' + Math.round(downPayment).toLocaleString();\n\n  const maxVal = Math.max(totalMortgage, totalTax, totalInsurance, totalHoa, downPayment);\n  document.getElementById('bar-mortgage').style.width = (totalMortgage / maxVal * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-tax').style.width = (totalTax / maxVal * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-insurance').style.width = (totalInsurance / maxVal * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-hoa').style.width = (totalHoa / maxVal * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-down').style.width = (downPayment / maxVal * 100) + '%';\n\n  const extra = totalCost - price;\n  const extraPct = Math.round((extra / price) * 100);\n\n  document.getElementById('home-insight').innerHTML = '\u003cdiv class=\"summary-icon\"\u003e🏠\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eA \u003cstrong\u003e$' + price.toLocaleString() + '\u003c/strong\u003e home actually costs \u003cstrong\u003e$' + Math.round(totalCost).toLocaleString() + '\u003c/strong\u003e over 30 years. That is \u003cstrong\u003e' + extraPct + '% more\u003c/strong\u003e than the sticker price once you factor in interest, taxes, insurance, and fees.\u003c/p\u003e';\n\n  \n  document.getElementById('monthly-home').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalMonthly).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('monthly-total').textContent = '$' + Math.round(totalMonthly + totalUtilities).toLocaleString();\n\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-mortgage').textContent = '$' + Math.round(mortgage).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-tax').textContent = '$' + Math.round(tax).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-insurance').textContent = '$' + Math.round(insurance).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-hoa').textContent = '$' + Math.round(hoa).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-elec').textContent = '$' + utilElec.toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-water').textContent = '$' + utilWater.toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-net').textContent = '$' + utilNet.toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('val-mo-trash').textContent = utilTrash \u003e 0 ? '$' + utilTrash.toLocaleString() : 'Included';\n\n  const maxMo = Math.max(mortgage, tax, insurance, hoa, utilElec, utilWater, utilNet, utilTrash || 1);\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-mortgage').style.width = (mortgage / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-tax').style.width = (tax / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-insurance').style.width = (insurance / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-hoa').style.width = (hoa / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-elec').style.width = (utilElec / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-water').style.width = (utilWater / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-net').style.width = (utilNet / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n  document.getElementById('bar-mo-trash').style.width = ((utilTrash || 1) / maxMo * 100) + '%';\n\n  const utilPct = Math.round((totalUtilities / (totalMonthly + totalUtilities)) * 100);\n  document.getElementById('monthly-insight').innerHTML = '\u003cdiv class=\"summary-icon\"\u003e💡\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eUtilities add \u003cstrong\u003e$' + totalUtilities.toLocaleString() + '/month\u003c/strong\u003e on top of home ownership costs. They make up \u003cstrong\u003e' + utilPct + '%\u003c/strong\u003e of your total monthly housing spending.\u003c/p\u003e';\n\n  const result = document.getElementById('home-result');\n  result.style.display = 'block';\n  result.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"info-section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-header\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"info-icon\"\u003e\n      \n      \u003csvg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"/\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWhat\u0026#39;s Included\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-body\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eOur calculator accounts for:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMortgage Payment\u003c/strong\u003e — Principal + interest based on your down payment and rate\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProperty Taxes\u003c/strong\u003e — Annual taxes divided monthly\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHome Insurance\u003c/strong\u003e — Estimated at 0.35% of home value annually\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHOA Fees\u003c/strong\u003e — Monthly association dues\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaintenance\u003c/strong\u003e — Estimated at 1% of home value annually\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTotal 30-Year Cost\u003c/strong\u003e — The shocking true number most buyers miss\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"info-section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-header\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"info-icon\"\u003e\n      \n      \u003csvg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M9 18h6\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M10 22h4\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 2.38 1.19 4.47 3 5.74V17h8v-2.26c1.81-1.27 3-3.36 3-5.74a7 7 0 0 0-7-7z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWhy This Matters\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-body\"\u003e\n    A $450,000 home doesn\u0026rsquo;t cost $450,000. Over 30 years, you\u0026rsquo;ll pay closer to \u003cstrong\u003e$900,000\u003c/strong\u003e when you factor in interest, taxes, and insurance. Know the real number before you buy.\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"info-section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-header\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"info-icon\"\u003e\n      \n      \u003csvg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cellipse cx=\"12\" cy=\"5\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"3\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eData Sources\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"info-section-body\"\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMortgage calculations: Standard amortization formula\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProperty tax rates: Tax Foundation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInsurance estimates: Industry averages\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eLast updated: June 28, 2026\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n"}